riod.</li><li data-v-882ffde4>Statement of study compliance</li><li data-v-882ffde4>Statement of confidentiality</li><li data-v-882ffde4>Statement of test facility management</li><li data-v-882ffde4>AAALAC Certificate.</li><li data-v-882ffde4>A copy of the final signed study plan and any amendments if any as an annexure.</li></p><p data-v-882ffde4><b data-v-882ffde4>Note:</b> If response from sponsor for finalization of draft report is not received within six months after sending draft report in spite of repeated reminders, management could approve termination of study, or finalization of report and archiving. In such an event, any subsequent requests from sponsor for modification, correction or addition to the final report will be subject to report amendment at additional cost.</p></div></div>", 1);
